docs.lead_paragraph: MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay, Aug. 5 -- The regime of Gen. Alfredo Stroessner is doing what it can to dress up democratically for the American foreign ministers' conference this month in Santiago, Chile. However, it is unlikely that the disguise will spare Paraguay from being classed as a dictatorship.
